    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - REMOVE - AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="3">
        <title>AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the auxiliary bearing retainer ring bolts (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301737">Figure 37</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301737" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301737" filename="../figg13/G1301737.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 37. Remove Ring Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the mainshaft rear groove snap ring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301737">Figure 37</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the splined washer from inside the auxiliary drive gear assembly (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301737">Figure 37</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Insert three (3) of the bolts in the specially tapped holes of the retainer ring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301737">Figure 37</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten the bolts evenly to force the auxiliary drive gear assembly from the case.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the auxiliary drive gear from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301738">Figure 38</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301738" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301738" filename="../figg13/G1301738.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 38. Auxiliary Drive Gear</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the splined washer from the mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301739">Figure 39</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301739" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301739" filename="../figg13/G1301739.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 39. Remove Splined Washer</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
